videos.headline: Rinne had a rare off night in Game 2
videos.description: Barry Melrose points to Pekka Rinne's Game 2 struggles and Anaheim's resiliency as the main reasons why the Ducks were able to even the series against the Predators.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Analysis (Rinne had a rare off night in Game 2) 2017/05/14 SC

videos.headline: Johansen on Kesler: 'I don't how you cheer for a guy like that'
videos.description: When asked if Ryan Kesler has gone over the line in the Western Conference finals, Ryan Johansen says "it doesn't make sense" how he plays the game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Interview (Johansen on Kesler: 'I don't how you cheer for a guy like that') 2017/05/14 ESHEET
